songs.title: AbandonedHouse
songs.lyrics:
Blacked out, cashed out
I ain't at the trap house
Bitch I’m at the bath house
Don't know how to act now
Always known to act out
Always want to lash out
Kickin' raps, rollin’ fast, flickin' off the ash now
Everybody wanna clap now
Drop it off your ass now
Show up to your dad's  house
Say click-clack take that ass out
I don't want a problem, all I want is what I need
Backwoods, water and a couple bricks of weed
I don't got a job but I get that money when I need
Couple things a week and I'm straight up on my feet
Blacked out, cashed out
I ain't at the trap house
Bitch I'm at the bath house
Don’t know how to act now
